subject: Fantasy Sports
Computers and the Internet
Football
lead_paragraph: Yahoo Inc. and the N.F.L. Players Association reached a settlement over the use of players’ statistics, photos and other data in Yahoo’s popular online fantasy football game, but details were not released.
